jeus.uddi.v2.api.request.inquiry

Class FindRelatedBusinesses

  • java.lang.Object
    • jeus.uddi.v2.AbstractRegistryObject
      • jeus.uddi.v2.api.request.inquiry.FindRelatedBusinesses
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, RegistryObject

    public class FindRelatedBusinesses
extends AbstractRegistryObject
    find_relatedBusinesses의 data type class. Used to locate information about businessEntity registrations that are related to a specific business entity whose key is passed in the inquiry.

    다음 schema는 UDDI version 2.0 Schema에서 인용한다.
